- **Other**: UUID, Event Logging, JSON Payloads


ğŸ“¬ API Endpoint
POST /api/wallet/add
Headers: Content-Type: application/json

Request Body:


{
  "wallet": "google",
  "receiptId": "12345",
  "userId": "user001"
}


Success Response:


{
  "message": "google wallet sync successful",
  "result": {
    "status": "Google Wallet sync done"
  }


